== Message Boxes ==
==== Delete ====
{{Msgbox
|id              = Msgbox:delete
|backgroundcolor = #fff3f3
|signal          = http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a1/Crystal_Clear_action_editdelete.png/48px-Crystal_Clear_action_editdelete.png
|heading         = This article should be ''deleted''.
|message         = It's useless or already exists elesewhere.}}
 <nowiki>{{msgbox:delete}}</nowiki>

==== Moved ====
{{Msgbox
|id              = Msgbox:moved
|backgroundcolor = #fff3f3
|signal          = http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Crystal_Clear_action_find.png/48px-Crystal_Clear_action_find.png
|heading         = This page can be deleted. Its content has been ''moved'' to [[{{{1}}}]]
|message         = It's not a redirect in order to avoid inconsistency. Don't link to me! }}
 <nowiki>{{msgbox:moved|asdf}} <!-- where 'asdf' is the article's new link --></nowiki>

==== Out of date ====
{{Msgbox
|id              = Msgbox:out of date
|backgroundcolor = #faf6ed
|signal          = http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/12/Crystal_Clear_app_clock.png/48px-Crystal_Clear_app_clock.png
|heading         = This article is ''out of date''.
|message         = Please help improve the wiki by updating the article to version {{{1}}} of LMMS.}}
 <nowiki>{{msgbox:out of date|xx}} <!-- where 'xx' is the version of LMMS it should about --></nowiki>

==== Too complex ====
